    --- Returns: Int.
    --- Summary: Provides the stdlib len int list operation using current Klang data types and runtime helpers.
    --- Contract: Preserve this typed interface when upgrading to a runtime-backed implementation.
    function LenIntList(value : List[Int]) : Int {
        return len(value);
    }

